message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with sound event detection and tracking. Other likely categories could be cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, and cs.NE. cs.LG and cs.AI are likely as the paper uses a neural network for the task. cs.CV is also possible as the paper deals with visual tracking of sound sources. cs.NE is possible as the paper uses a recurrent neural network.
